    dc:description "FIGURE 101. Botachus cylindratus Thorell, 1859 female. A, habitus, right; B, caudal ramus, medial; C, leg 1; D, leg 2; E, exopod of leg 3; F, leg 4; G, leg 5. Scale bars: A, 0.2 mm; B-G, 002 mm." ;
