    dc:description "FIGURE 102. Botachus cylindratus Thorell, 1859 male. A, habitus, right; B, proximal part of urosome showing legs 5 and 6, ventral; C, caudal ramus, dorsal; D, caudal ramus, right; E, leg 1; F, leg 2; G, leg 3; H, protopod and endopod of leg 4. Scale bars: A, 0.1 mm; B-H, 0.02 mm." ;
